window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Ruthless. Arrogant. Ice cold.</p> <p>Everyone warned me that the CFO of McCord Media was a nightmare to work for. I knew it going in, but I figured I could keep my head down and stay under Cole McCord’s radar.</p> <p>I figured wrong.</p> <p>Because a month before I started as his assistant, Mr. Ruthless and I spent one scorching hot night together in bed.</p> <p>In my defense, I had no idea that the gorgeous stranger I hooked up with at my girlfriend's birthday party would turn out to be my new boss. But company policy forbids work relationships, so it’s strictly business from now on.</p> <p>If only we could stop falling into bed together.</p> <p>If only he didn’t make me feel things I’ve never felt before.</p> <p>If only he wasn’t keeping a secret that could destroy us both.</p> <p><i>Author's note: Fall Into You is a standalone romance with dark themes and spicy bedroom scenes intended for mature listeners only.</i></p>"; 
